title: The Smashing eBook Series EPUB+MOBI+PDF
description:
Series - The Smashing eBook Series 

Year : 2010-2011 Genre : A Practical Guide Publisher : Smashing Media GmbH, Freiburg, Germany Language : English Format : PDF (all editions), MOBI, EPUB (starting from the third issue) Quality : Originally Computer (eBook) Description : Now you can Get all the eBooks Released by Smashing Magazine all in one swoop! The Smashing eBook Super Bundle contains the following eBooks: Successful Freelancing for Web Designers, Mastering Photoshop for Web Design, Mobile Design for iPhone and iPad, How to Create Selling E-Commerce Websites, Getting the Hang of Web Typography, Professional Web Design Volume 2, and Mastering Photoshop for Web Design Volume 2. A series of e-books about design and designing websites, produced by the German published by Smashing Media GmbH. In the release includes the best materials of the journal Smashing Magazine.
